then it will mean trouble.

01:08:00.616 --> 01:08:06.032
Brother Paras. I am searching
for my husband.

01:08:06.532 --> 01:08:08.741
I came from London in this
condition all alone.

01:08:09.241 --> 01:08:12.366
I just need an answer for my child..

01:08:12.866 --> 01:08:15.907
..that what happened to his father.

01:08:16.407 --> 01:08:19.907
I cannot force you, but...please help us.

01:08:26.324 --> 01:08:26.657
Tell me.

01:08:27.157 --> 01:08:31.157
Have you heard about Milan Damji? - Who?

01:08:31.657 --> 01:08:34.532
Milan Damji. No.

01:08:35.032 --> 01:08:37.407
Two years ago, on 25th May..

01:08:37.907 --> 01:08:40.699
..Bombay blood group was
required in Ekbalpur Nursing Home.

01:08:41.199 --> 01:08:41.824
What for?

01:08:42.324 --> 01:08:43.491
We just need to find that out.

01:08:43.991 --> 01:08:47.491
Can you do that?

01:08:53.866 --> 01:08:57.366
Laundry, sister.

01:08:59.574 --> 01:09:00.074
Laundry, sister.

01:09:00.574 --> 01:09:04.074
I am not laundry sister, I am sister Bidya.

01:09:06.657 --> 01:09:09.116
Your transistor is giving chocolate.

01:09:09.616 --> 01:09:10.074
Such a big chocolate.

01:09:10.574 --> 01:09:12.074
So big.

01:09:12.574 --> 01:09:13.324
Hello.

01:09:13.824 --> 01:09:16.991
You did disturb me, I am in a important meeting.

01:09:17.491 --> 01:09:20.449
In the room with Bishnu.

01:09:20.949 --> 01:09:24.449
Really? When?

01:09:30.741 --> 01:09:33.116
25th May, 2008.

01:09:33.616 --> 01:09:35.824
Two men had a meeting here.

01:09:36.324 --> 01:09:42.407
There was news about only two
people's death until now.

01:09:42.907 --> 01:09:46.116
But it seems like there
was a third person as well.

01:09:46.616 --> 01:09:50.241
And the blood was ordered from
Ekbalpur Nursing Home..

01:09:50.741 --> 01:09:51.699
..for this third person.

01:09:52.199 --> 01:09:53.741
So, was that third person Milan Damji?

01:09:54.241 --> 01:09:56.199
I don't have anymore information.

01:09:56.699 --> 01:09:57.532
Paras. Paras.

01:09:58.032 --> 01:09:59.074
Just a minute.

01:09:59.574 --> 01:10:00.907
You will find the rest of the information..

01:10:01.407 --> 01:10:04.282
..at Park Street Police Station
or find Dr. Ganguly.

01:10:04.782 --> 01:10:08.282
That night he was on night duty.

01:10:12.032 --> 01:10:13.241
No record.

01:10:13.741 --> 01:10:15.324
I remember that it was a police case..

01:10:15.824 --> 01:10:18.324
..but I don't remember what exactly it was.

01:10:18.824 --> 01:10:19.616
It was two years ago. - Ready, sir.

01:10:20.116 --> 01:10:21.366
Yes, I will be there. - Okay.

01:10:21.866 --> 01:10:23.949
Give me a day, I will check and tell you.

01:10:24.449 --> 01:10:25.032
Thank you.
- I need to go, I have a surgery.

01:10:25.532 --> 01:10:29.032
Thank you.

01:10:38.074 --> 01:10:38.616
Don't worry. - Okay.

01:10:39.116 --> 01:10:39.657
Please. - Thank you, thank you.

01:10:40.157 --> 01:10:43.657
Thank you very much.

01:10:55.491 --> 01:10:56.532
Yes.

01:10:57.032 --> 01:10:58.491
Dr. Ganguly? - Yes.

01:10:58.991 --> 01:11:01.032
Hello. Bob Biswas.

01:11:01.532 --> 01:11:01.991
Hello.

01:11:02.491 --> 01:11:05.991
Just a minute.

01:11:09.199 --> 01:11:13.032
'I remember that it was a police case.'

01:11:13.532 --> 01:11:14.491
Stop it Rana.

01:11:14.991 --> 01:11:18.032
The commotion outside and then this.

01:11:18.532 --> 01:11:19.824
Mr. Chatterjee. - What?

01:11:20.324 --> 01:11:21.907
Hello. - Oh my, God.

01:11:22.407 --> 01:11:22.741
Bidya Bagchi.

01:11:23.241 --> 01:11:24.532
You arrived at the right time. - Hi, Rana.

01:11:25.032 --> 01:11:27.199
You had shut this computer up the other day,
didn't you? - Yes.

01:11:27.699 --> 01:11:28.282
Do it today as well, please, - Sure.

01:11:28.782 --> 01:11:29.907
Otherwise I will go crazy.

01:11:30.407 --> 01:11:30.741
Thank you.

01:11:31.241 --> 01:11:34.116
I will go meet the senior officer.

01:11:34.616 --> 01:11:34.824
Come, come.

01:11:35.324 --> 01:11:36.032
Oh, God.

01:11:36.532 --> 01:11:37.116
No, no, keep seated.

