01:11:47.407 --> 01:11:50.116
..who was a police informer in the Metro attack case.

01:11:50.616 --> 01:11:53.782
And second..

01:11:54.282 --> 01:11:57.157
Second was Vijay Verma who
was a government agent.

01:11:57.657 --> 01:12:01.157
Government agent?

01:12:02.491 --> 01:12:06.074
He's back, he's back.

01:12:06.574 --> 01:12:07.199
It's done, sir.

01:12:07.699 --> 01:12:09.699
Done, Mr. Chatterjee. - Its, done.

01:12:10.199 --> 01:12:11.616
That's nice, very good.

01:12:12.116 --> 01:12:12.449
Thank you, thank you.

01:12:12.949 --> 01:12:13.741
Thank you. - Welcome.

01:12:14.241 --> 01:12:16.657
Okay.

01:12:17.157 --> 01:12:17.699
What is the matter?

01:12:18.199 --> 01:12:21.907
Mr. Chatterjee, may I leave? - Yes.

01:12:22.407 --> 01:12:22.532
Bye.

01:12:23.032 --> 01:12:26.532
Bye.

01:13:02.157 --> 01:13:03.574
Yes, mother.

