01:13:38.771 --> 01:13:39.349
Anybody there?

01:13:39.449 --> 01:13:40.699
I do the cleaning myself at home.

01:13:41.199 --> 01:13:43.699
Sit. I cannot tolerate dust.

01:13:44.199 --> 01:13:44.991
Pull a chair.

01:13:45.491 --> 01:13:47.741
Speak, Satyaki Sinha.

01:13:48.241 --> 01:13:49.782
Mrs. Bagchi, I pursued the information..

01:13:50.282 --> 01:13:50.741
..acquired from the database.

01:13:51.241 --> 01:13:53.282
There is no mention of a
third person in the records

01:13:53.782 --> 01:13:56.699
Dr. Ganguly, Milan Damji,
Ekbalpur Nursing Home.

01:13:57.199 --> 01:13:58.991
No one knows anything about it.

01:13:59.491 --> 01:14:01.991
There are records of Vijay and Dinesh.

01:14:02.491 --> 01:14:04.116
Vijay Verma was investigating
the Metro attack..

01:14:04.616 --> 01:14:06.491
