01:14:44.616 --> 01:14:45.532
Just like Milan Damji..

01:14:46.032 --> 01:14:48.032
..even Vijay Verma worked for NDC.

01:14:48.532 --> 01:14:52.032
To hide his true identity.

01:14:55.282 --> 01:14:57.407
It must be him, take a good look.

01:14:57.907 --> 01:14:59.907
No. it wasn't him.

