What? - The suitcase.

01:15:26.949 --> 01:15:29.699
It was him, sister.

01:15:30.199 --> 01:15:33.199
Are you sure? - Sure, it was him.

01:15:33.699 --> 01:15:35.199
Who was he? - I don't know.

01:15:35.699 --> 01:15:37.824
I suggest that you take Poltu home..

01:15:38.324 --> 01:15:41.032
..until then I will find out, okay. - Yes.

01:15:41.532 --> 01:15:43.074
Good morning, sir.

01:15:43.574 --> 01:15:46.032
Good morning, sir.

01:15:46.532 --> 01:15:50.032
Good morning.

