Listen, when Rana arrives will you ask him to call me.

01:16:46.491 --> 01:16:47.282
The police officer? - Yes.

01:16:47.782 --> 01:16:49.032
Okay. - Yes, fine.

01:16:49.532 --> 01:16:53.032
Bye.

01:17:22.449 --> 01:17:22.616
Sorry.

