Stop. Stop.

01:18:58.616 --> 01:19:02.116
Stop.

01:19:18.491 --> 01:19:19.032
Oh, God.

01:19:19.532 --> 01:19:21.741
Mrs. Bagchi, Bob Biswas
was a contract killer.

01:19:22.241 --> 01:19:22.616
This is his phone.

01:19:23.116 --> 01:19:25.491
And I have found these
photographs from his phone.

01:19:25.991 --> 01:19:27.491
Agnes D'Mello.

01:19:27.991 --> 01:19:29.741
Dr. Ganguly.

01:19:30.241 --> 01:19:31.116
And after that...you.

01:19:31.616 --> 01:19:32.116
This time you survived.

01:19:32.616 --> 01:19:33.991
But the man who hired Bob..

01:19:34.491 --> 01:19:36.032
..doesn't want anyone to
reach Milan Damji..

